  "name": "Building Blocks - Cultural Heritage Building Blocks",
  "abstract": "Reusable OGC Building Blocks for modelling cultural heritage data, covering heritage objects,\ndigital representations, provenance, sensor observations and dataset metadata.\n",
  "description": "This register defines reusable, machine-readable specification components for the cultural\nheritage domain, building on CIDOC-CRM, PROV-O, SOSA/SSN, EDM and DCAT. It originated from the\nstandards profiling work of the [HERITALISE](https://heritalise.eu) project (deliverables D8.1\nand D8.2), but is intended as a general-purpose register usable beyond that project.\n",
  "modified": "2026-06-25T14:31:05.207132",
  "tooling": {
    "bblocks-postprocess": {
      "commitId": "\"63a70437bf8124dfddbdd444f28013fb2c0ecb1f",
