      "abstract": "A scientific observation or measurement of a heritage object or place \u2014 environmental monitoring, condition assessment, conservation science \u2014 modelled as a CIDOC-CRM E16 Measurement (the entry point CRMsci specialises for scientific observation) and profiling the PROV-O Activity. Bridges sensor data recorded via the OGC SensorThings API back into the CIDOC-CRM graph.",
